column2: SELECT    tab1.pra,tab1.pdec,distance.n1 FROM( SELECT    n.objID, n.distance, n.type,   p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r,   pz.z as photoz FROM Galaxy AS G   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS n   LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid=p.objid   LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid=pz.objid   WHERE G.objID = n.objID ) AS tab1 JOIN ( SELECT dbo.fCosmoComovDist2ObjectsRADEC(#,#,#,tab1.photoz,tab1.pra,tab1.pdec,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT) as n1   ) AS distance ON distance.n1<#
